Type: Package
Package: carnaval
Title: Access datasets of Brazilian Samba Schools and color palettes in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Icaro Bernardes", "dos Santos Coutinho", , "icaro@bitanalytics.dev.br", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download data on Samba Schools of Brazil. The data spans
    almost a century of carnaval competitions scores, judges, rules and so
    on.  Palettes based on the Samba Schools colors are provided as well.
